<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font></P>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">October 3, 2003 | Page 11

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><B><P>OTHER STORIES BELOW:</B><BR>
<A HREF="#NWU">National Writers Union</A><BR>
<A HREF="#Congress">Congress Hotel</A><BR>
